def_cn: 彻底清理(橱柜、房间、容器等);把…打扫干净
def_en: If you clean out something such as a cupboard, room, or container, you take everything out of it and clean the inside of it thoroughly.
If someone cleans you out, they take all the money and valuables you have. If they clean out a place, they take everything of value that is in it.
